&lt;div class="sect2"&gt;
&lt;h3 id="_how_can_i_obtain_the_plugin"&gt;How can I obtain the plugin?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="paragraph"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Just like any other Grails plugin, through the Grails Plugin center.
Edit your project&amp;#8217;s build.gradle file, by adding the plugin&amp;#8217;s dependency declaration:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="listingblock"&gt;
&lt;div class="content"&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;dependencies {
    ...
    compile "org.grails.plugins:elasticsearch:3.0.0.M1"
    ...

}&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
