&lt;h1&gt;i18n-enums&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Successor for the Grails 2.x plugin. Now ported to Grails 3.x&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This plugin adds an annotation usable on Enums to easy add and implement the MessageSourceResolvable interface in an standard way throughout a project.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Documentation can be found here: http://sbglasius.github.io/i18n-enums/&;lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1&gt;Render all Grails i18n messages to Javascript&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;This plugin includes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;i18nService to get all messages from messageSource bean&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;i18nJs taglib to render in GSP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;I18nJsController to get JSON object in Javascript app&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Install&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Add to build.gradle&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;dependencies {
     compile &amp;quot;org.grails.plugins:i18n-javascript:0.4.2&amp;quot;
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Config&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In application.groovy add config with desired including and excluding prefixes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;i18nJs {
    prefixInclude = [
        'i18nJs'
    ]

    prefixExclude = [
        'default', 'other'
    ]
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So 'i18nJs.page1.header' will be rendered whereas 'default.home.label' will not.
Without this all items from message.properties wiil be in JS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Get messages&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In GSP use&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;g:i18nJs/&amp;gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;to render all messages in output HTML&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Or make request to /I18nJs/getMessages within AJAX call.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Usage&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;alert(I18N.getMessage('my.message.code'));
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

