&lt;h1&gt;Grails Postgresql Extensions&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;THIS BRANCH (master) IS FOR GRAILS 4 AND HIBERNATE 5.4&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://bintray.com/kaleidos/plugins/postgresql-extensions/4.8.0/link";&gt;&lt;img src="https://api.bintray.com/packages/kaleidos/plugins/postgresql-extensions/images/download.svg?version=4.8.0"; alt="Download" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://bintray.com/kaleidos/plugins/postgresql-extensions/5.3.0/link";&gt;&lt;img src="https://api.bintray.com/packages/kaleidos/plugins/postgresql-extensions/images/download.svg?version=5.3.0"; alt="Download" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://bintray.com/kaleidos/plugins/postgresql-extensions/6.1.0/link";&gt;&lt;img src="https://api.bintray.com/packages/kaleidos/plugins/postgresql-extensions/images/download.svg?version=6.1.0"; alt="Download" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://bintray.com/kaleidos/plugins/postgresql-extensions/7.0.0/link";&gt;&lt;img src="https://api.bintray.com/packages/kaleidos/plugins/postgresql-extensions/images/download.svg?version=7.0.0"; alt="Download" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://travis-ci.org/kaleidos/grails-postgresql-extensions";&gt;&lt;img src="https://travis-ci.org/kaleidos/grails-postgresql-extensions.svg?branch=master"; alt="Build Status" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a grails plugin that provides hibernate user types to use Postgresql native types such as Array, Hstore, Json,
Jsonb... from a Grails application. It also provides new criterias to query this new native types.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Currently the plugin supports array, hstore, json and jsonb fields as well as some query methods.
More native types and query methods will be added in the future.&lt;/p&gt;
